# Silly Method (Brute Force)

Kid says:

“Let me check every group of 3!”

Try:

```text
(-1,0,1)
(-1,0,2)
(-1,1,2)
```

And every possible combination.

This works…

BUT TOO SLOW 😭

Because:

For every number → check every number → check every number.

Time Complexity:

```text
