# Important Trick — Remove Duplicates

See:

```text
[-1,-1]
```

If we repeat same number again:

We may get same answer again.

Interviewers hate duplicates.

So skip repeated numbers.

Example:

```text
if(nums[i] == nums[i-1])
continue;
```

---

# Golden Rule

When checking 3 numbers:

### Sum < 0

Need bigger number.

Move LEFT →

---

### Sum > 0

Too big.

Move RIGHT ←

---

### Sum == 0

🎉 Found answer

Store it and move both.

---

## Visual Memory Trick


Too small → move LEFT
Too big   → move RIGHT
Equal 0   → save answer
```

Because array is sorted.

